Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.00,0:01:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分開了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.73,0:01:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這座山因為被邪惡帝皇\N多惡達支配的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.27,0:01:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連彩虹的顏色也變了黑白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們邊和多惡達的魔神戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.31,0:01:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令第一界層和第二界層\N恢復原來的和平世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧,彩虹的顏色\N已有兩條復原了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.46,0:01:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是去到第二界層\N也復原了的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.02,0:02:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後,我們現身處的是這裏\N第三界層的酷熱世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達的魔神也很強勁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.18,0:02:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.20,0:02:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十四話\N百人力量是僊人力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.32,0:02:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔芝達\N渡他們已侵入了這熱島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.42,0:02:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔芝達\N不可以讓他們接近熱山的山頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不可以失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在這個熱島把他們收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所也所也大人,請交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.93,0:02:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算要了我的命\N我也定會把渡他們收拾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熱得我受不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.80,0:02:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔芝達\N第一山寨便交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.91,0:03:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在第二山寨守護灼熱之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單純的力量,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.11,0:03:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.95,0:03:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達大人的憤怒\N已像這熱島一樣在猛燒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們彼此也不能再失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.04,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.05,0:03:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在鐵板上跳舞的樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.58,0:03:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是笑的時候啊\N師傅你不熱嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點也不,那秘密是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石造的鞋?真狡猾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼時候\N只造了自己那對的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好呢,也造一對給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.09,0:03:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.00,0:03:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了\N這邊的是渡的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害!厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.63,0:04:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,極寒之劍和灼熱之盾\N會在哪裏啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.88,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的熱力\N長期在這裏會死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.59,0:04:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非要盡快找到不可\N先上山頂看看全島的環境吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.54,0:04:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心了,在這種地方受襲\N沒有地方逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.44,0:04:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.92,0:04:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.73,0:04:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前後夾擊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.47,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.00,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,波子機之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中大獎,全是火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.21,0:05:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.80,0:05:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進去這裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,快點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉我進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿你沒辦法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全中!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.75,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?失敗了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.17,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們收拾不了渡的話\N便由我去收拾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.57,0:05:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,這樣他們定會變燒豬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.50,0:05:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一看便知道了吧\N在放路牌…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽錯了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼時候在這裏的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.27,0:06:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!這個路牌…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畫上了劍和盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.02,0:06:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說的話極寒之劍和灼熱之盾\N是在這邊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧,師傅\N古拿瑪也快點來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的傢伙追來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…\N鳥先生,一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蛋,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.21,0:06:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蛋\N把噴火的地方全部塞住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在,快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得好,回來吧,小蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.41,0:07:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,石鞋已支持不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!看啊\N這附近不是太熱啊,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.08,0:07:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是樂天的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.57,0:07:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是第一山寨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一山寨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪知道得真清楚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.09,0:07:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生什麼也知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.60,0:07:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說創界山\N沒有我不知道的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的什麼也知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.60,0:07:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如有關創界山的事我不知道\N要我剪光頭也沒問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.28,0:07:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼這個山寨的入口\N在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在那邊吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害!厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏怎會這樣的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.05,0:08:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,籠門便是出口了\N想進去便要突破我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!我求之不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.00,0:08:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生,你去哪裏啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手!放手啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.12,0:08:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.80,0:08:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.30,0:08:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣結束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.70,0:08:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想得美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,盡快收拾他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿過那到門便成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.41,0:09:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們收拾你吧\N陣式,兩面夾擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰神丸\N對,你可以盡快來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸\N那便是終點了,上啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們啊,用下一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.33,0:10:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣式,毛蟲陣法,大火球!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,用炎龍拳吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.60,0:10:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!\N炎龍拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.70,0:10:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.34,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我記著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.30,0:11:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這聲音和在第一界層\N得到的神部之笛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在發光!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是被呼喚的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.06,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你也吹吹看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在睡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.41,0:12:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和亞撒姆一模一樣\N這支笛,這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.03,0:12:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救世主終於來救我了\N真是感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.86,0:12:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的笛聲\N把這顆球的封印解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,封印?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被困在這球裏面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為受罰而被困在裏面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說什麼?\N我曾經是這個島上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.95,0:12:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護著極寒之劍和灼熱之盾\N的百人僊人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心你的說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾經守護?\N請你把原因告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.55,0:13:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久以前\N這裏是個叫加蓮島的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是第三界層中最美的島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.26,0:13:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還有由亞撒姆像\N拿著擁有寒冷力量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.10,0:13:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極寒之劍\N和控制熱力的灼熱之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令這個世界的氣溫平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.81,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是多惡達用灼熱之劍\N換了極寒之劍後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏便變成了\N誰也不能住的灼熱地獄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.65,0:13:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼只要再把灼熱之劍\N和極寒之劍交換的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便能令第三界層復原了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是很簡單嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,去把灼熱之劍交換吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡單、簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可惜\N因為由火炎牆的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不能接近亞撒姆像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有極寒之劍\N便也許有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.61,0:13:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?\N那我們先去找極寒之劍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢!對呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是極寒之間\N也不知所蹤了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.90,0:14:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫渡吧?請你無論怎樣\N也要令這世界恢復原狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.80,0:14:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和亞撒姆像一模一樣的你\N一定可以做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…要怎樣做才好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.25,0:14:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下不妙了\N現在只有做一做戲騙他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!是古拿瑪\N在這裏啊,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.60,0:14:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了第三界層的波士\N所也所也的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.12,0:14:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!\N他也許會知道極寒之劍在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,他在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.37,0:15:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果戰神丸在的話\N便可以一起去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.03,0:15:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生不一起去\N渡會認識路嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.24,0:15:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的熱力\N如果沒有魔神便去不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次渡也一定玩完了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.80,0:15:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然\N不是由我直接出手不行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是真熱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.93,0:15:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果把極寒之劍\N拿到手的話便會變涼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果渡找到便好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能會找到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.80,0:15:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪\N你不知道極寒之劍在哪裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.03,0:15:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生也有不知道的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.44,0:15:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.76,0:16:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰說過\N如果有關創界山的事不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剃光頭也可以的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.20,0:16:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪也沒有線索呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要照約定剃光頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.01,0:16:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\N我對於不知道的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.18,0:16:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧,你還是不知道\N極寒之劍在哪裏吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.80,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生說謊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.70,0:16:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!你說住口?好吧?\N在下替你剃光頭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手,我什麼都不知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼極寒之劍在哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.64,0:16:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,你覺悟吧\N光頭是很涼快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…等等,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂動的話會連頭也切下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野武牛一郎流,光頭斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手!\N極寒之劍是在第四界層啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.47,0:17:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛才說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?第四界層?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.70,0:17:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話\N不論渡怎樣也找不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去通知他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.26,0:17:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…等一等,請你也帶我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.41,0:17:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!你幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.24,0:17:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,轉換之術\N公公,走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.51,0:17:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.80,0:17:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在右腳未落地前\N舉起左腳便不會熱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以控制他嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了,出發,公公!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真蠢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有向前進了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.50,0:18:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你的命也到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你便是第三界層的波士嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實點\N把極寒之劍所在地告訴我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真蠢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看不見對方的動作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題\N這樣下去追不到他的動作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也加速吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.00,0:18:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.50,0:18:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有機會!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油!龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.75,0:19:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,用這武器試試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛龍拳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.05,0:19:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.31,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛龍拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.60,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!極寒之劍在第四界層\N是鳥先生他告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古…古拿瑪背叛了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.74,0:19:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四界層?龍神丸\N怎樣可以上到第四界層?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.46,0:19:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三界層的彩虹不恢復原狀\N是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼不是不能去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我來幫你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.65,0:19:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,百人僊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.20,0:19:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就正如這個名字一樣\N我擁有一百個人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達也是因此才把我封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就用那個力量\N前往第四界層吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩,不過可能力量還是不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡\N我也用全部力量試試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.69,0:20:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你應該在第二界層\N得到真實之鏡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用它映照亞撒姆像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.62,0:20:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真實之鏡?但是要怎樣做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.70,0:20:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我吧,知道嗎?\N能看見亞撒姆像只有一瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.52,0:20:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要瞄準啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個了,快點把它照下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.27,0:20:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.12,0:20:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.00,0:21:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,把劍舉起來吧\N我要用力量送你到第四界層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.60,0:21:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,火美子\N你替我告訴師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我定會把極寒之劍取回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.87,0:21:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.14,0:21:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以分心!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.14,0:21:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.50,0:21:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去啊!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.05,0:21:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要放手!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.12,0:21:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!

